# ğŸ§ª API Testing Automation (Playwright + TypeScript + Faker)

This project demonstrates **API automation testing** using **Playwright**, **TypeScript**, and **Axios**, following a **modular and scalable structure**.  
It covers complete CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) flow with both **live API** and **faker-based local simulation**.

